headline: MOS Potash Revenues Dip Y/Y in Oct-Nov, Phosphate & Fertilizantes Up
summary: Mosaic witnesses a delay in Canpotex shipments in the first two months of the fourth quarter of 2024 due to Canadian rail and port strikes, impacting potash sales volumes.
